@node Legacy Registry
@section §2.1 — Legacy Metallurgical Registry (pre-v1.2)
Projects named before the v1.2 convention drew from metallurgy,
materials science, and industrial forging. These names are
@strong{preserved as-is} unless explicitly renamed by the maintainer.
The v1.2 convention applies prospectively --- no forced back-rename.

